{"tid":1398923,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［85罷工］馬會員工給CEO的公開信","createTime":"2019-08-03T03:50:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-03T04:45:30.000Z","uid":282445,"like":22,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"71d5259a1a1f5334f5fb02d6d26c9769c0025f0b","tid":1398923,"uid":282445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T03:50:55.000Z","msg":"琴日喺另一位ching個po見到好多同事po晒證出黎，證明大家雖然身在呢間咁建制嘅公司，但仍然好有骨氣！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n今日我同一班同事就準備左另一波攻勢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，寫一封公開信俾應家柏同周永健，驚大家tldr，我簡單撮要以下幾點（全文拉落底有link)：<br />\n<br />\n1、以主席/行政總裁名義，公開促請林鄭月娥答應市民五大訴求<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n2、自元朗恐襲後，警黑涉嫌包庇勾結，嚴重影響市民對警察信任，為免出現不必要衝突，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">現促請馬會取消警員駐守馬場，改由馬會保安人員自行負責。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n3、林鄭月娥踐踏公義丶蔑視民意，對受傷及自殺的市民，從未展現出應有的關懷，用拖延手法試圖扭轉民意，根本沒有誠意去解決矛盾。有鑑於此，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我們一群員工公開正式要求馬會取消開鑼日特首盃賽事。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n</span></span><br />\n4、我們希望馬會主席及行政總裁，在八月十四日前作公開回覆，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">若有關人士未能對上述三丶四丶五項作出具體回應，我們會進行按章工作，並且積極考慮以罷工方式作嚴正抗議。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n我知有同事質疑有冇用，馬會唔會理你啦etc. 大家要記得，我地唔係睇到希望先要堅持，而係堅持落去先會有希望！<br />\n<br />\n封信今日出街，蘋果同立場有報導：<br />\n<a href=\"https://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20190803&amp;s=6996647&amp;a=59891433\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20190803%26s%3D6996647%26a%3D59891433&d=JkVIzhDRZadGdMc0KemjDUB1UtkZy1G9%2FYekDAkGV2Y%3D&h=228d8775\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20190803%26s%3D6996647%26a%3D59891433&h=8afb058d\" target=\"_blank\">https://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20190803&amp;s=6996647&amp;a=59891433</a><br />\n<br />\n[url]<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/馬會員工促管理層取消警員駐馬場-取消開鑼日特首盃-8-14-前不回應按章工作及考慮罷工/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E9%A6%AC%E6%9C%83%E5%93%A1%E5%B7%A5%E4%BF%83%E7%AE%A1%E7%90%86%E5%B1%A4%E5%8F%96%E6%B6%88%E8%AD%A6%E5%93%A1%E9%A7%90%E9%A6%AC%E5%A0%B4-%E5%8F%96%E6%B6%88%E9%96%8B%E9%91%BC%E6%97%A5%E7%89%B9%E9%A6%96%E7%9B%83-8-14-%E5%89%8D%E4%B8%8D%E5%9B%9E%E6%87%89%E6%8C%89%E7%AB%A0%E5%B7%A5%E4%BD%9C%E5%8F%8A%E8%80%83%E6%85%AE%E7%BD%B7%E5%B7%A5%2F&d=JkVIzhDRZadGdMc0KemjDUB1UtkZy1G9%2FYekDAkGV2Y%3D&h=8808d981\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E9%A6%AC%E6%9C%83%E5%93%A1%E5%B7%A5%E4%BF%83%E7%AE%A1%E7%90%86%E5%B1%A4%E5%8F%96%E6%B6%88%E8%AD%A6%E5%93%A1%E9%A7%90%E9%A6%AC%E5%A0%B4-%E5%8F%96%E6%B6%88%E9%96%8B%E9%91%BC%E6%97%A5%E7%89%B9%E9%A6%96%E7%9B%83-8-14-%E5%89%8D%E4%B8%8D%E5%9B%9E%E6%87%89%E6%8C%89%E7%AB%A0%E5%B7%A5%E4%BD%9C%E5%8F%8A%E8%80%83%E6%85%AE%E7%BD%B7%E5%B7%A5%2F&h=058c62bc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/politics/馬會員工促管理層取消警員駐馬場-取消開鑼日特首盃-8-14-前不回應按章工作及考慮罷工/</a><br />\n[/url]<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">各部門同事想加入聯署嘅話，可以喺度留張員工證相 （記得遮樣遮badge no.) 亦都歡迎各界市民聯署，link在此，請fb, ig同我瘋狂廣傳</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSeS51SCdIt_iSveF_UzA-fQhm0qKftYQ5Q62JF2dasU2EzEMQ/viewform\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fforms%2Fd%2Fe%2F1FAIpQLSeS51SCdIt_iSveF_UzA-fQhm0qKftYQ5Q62JF2dasU2EzEMQ%2Fviewform&d=JkVIzhDRZadGdMc0KemjDUB1UtkZy1G9%2FYekDAkGV2Y%3D&h=8bf9a1a4\" target=\"_bl